data.description:
This stunning POOL WITH LAKE VIEW home is a dream come true for anyone seeking a spacious and elegant living space. One of the standout features of this home is the bonus room that's pre wired for surround sound, a versatile space that can be customized to meet your specific needs. Whether you envision a home office, a playroom for the kids, or a cozy reading nook, the possibilities are endless. The bonus room, like the rest of the home, is flooded with natural light and a spacious floor plan with 2761 square feet of living area. Including a huge living room, a kitchen with beautiful granite counter top, extra-large master suite with separate tub and shower, double sinks, large walk-in closet with custom built-ins, tray ceilings in master room. Located in the desirable gated community of Hammock Trace Preserve just minutes away from popular shopping, restaurants, businesses,  and world famous beaches.
Lawn care paid for through the remaining of 2024 by sellers.
